'''Indona''' was a continent on the planet [[Cholganna/Legends|Cholganna]]. The [[Nexu/Legends|nexu]] was native to its forests before being imported offworld.<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Alien Species">''[[The New Essential Guide to Alien Species]]''</ref>

